{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"There was a time in my life"},{"time":3000,"text":"when everything seemed perfect."},{"time":6000,"text":"Everywhere I went, I felt at home."},{"time":8000,"text":"Everyone I met,"},{"time":10000,"text":"I felt I knew them for as long as I could remember."},{"time":13000,"text":"And I want to share with you how I came to that place"},{"time":16000,"text":"and what I've learned since I left it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":18000,"text":"This is where it began."},{"time":21000,"text":"And it raises an existential question,"},{"time":23000,"text":"which is, if I'm having this experience of complete connection and full consciousness,"},{"time":26000,"text":"why am I not visible in the photograph,"},{"time":29000,"text":"and where is this time and place?"},{"time":32000,"text":"This is Los Angeles, California, where I live."},{"time":35000,"text":"This is a police photo. That's actually my car."},{"time":38000,"text":"We're less than a mile from one of the largest hospitals in Los Angeles,"},{"time":41000,"text":"called Cedars-Sinai."},{"time":43000,"text":"And the situation is that a car full of paramedics"},{"time":45000,"text":"on their way home from the hospital after work"},{"time":48000,"text":"have run across the wreckage,"},{"time":50000,"text":"and they've advised the police"},{"time":52000,"text":"that there were no survivors inside the car,"},{"time":54000,"text":"that the driver's dead, that I'm dead."},{"time":57000,"text":"And the police are waiting for the fire department to arrive"},{"time":60000,"text":"to cut apart the vehicle"},{"time":62000,"text":"to extract the body of the driver."},{"time":64000,"text":"And when they do, they find that behind the glass,"},{"time":67000,"text":"they find me."},{"time":69000,"text":"And my skull's crushed and my collar bone is crushed;"},{"time":71000,"text":"all but two of my ribs,"},{"time":73000,"text":"my pelvis and both arms --"},{"time":75000,"text":"they're all crushed, but there is still a pulse."},{"time":78000,"text":"And they get me to that nearby hospital,"},{"time":80000,"text":"Cedars-Sinai,"},{"time":82000,"text":"where that night I receive, because of my internal bleeding,"},{"time":85000,"text":"45 units of blood --"},{"time":87000,"text":"which means full replacements of all the blood in me --"},{"time":89000,"text":"before they're able to staunch the flow."},{"time":91000,"text":"I'm put on full life support,"},{"time":93000,"text":"and I have a massive stroke,"},{"time":96000,"text":"and my brain drops into a coma."}]},{"cues":[{"time":98000,"text":"Now comas are measured"},{"time":100000,"text":"on a scale from 15 down to three."},{"time":102000,"text":"Fifteen is a mild coma. Three is the deepest."},{"time":105000,"text":"And if you look, you'll see that there's only one way you can score three."},{"time":108000,"text":"It's essentially there's no sign of life"},{"time":110000,"text":"from outside at all."},{"time":112000,"text":"I spent more than a month in a Glasgow Coma Scale three,"},{"time":115000,"text":"and it is inside that deepest level of coma,"},{"time":117000,"text":"on the rim between my life and my death,"},{"time":120000,"text":"that I'm experiencing the full connection and full consciousness"},{"time":123000,"text":"of inner space."}]},{"cues":[{"time":125000,"text":"From my family looking in from outside,"},{"time":128000,"text":"what they're trying to figure out"},{"time":130000,"text":"is a different kind of existential question,"},{"time":133000,"text":"which is, how far is it going to be possible to bridge"},{"time":136000,"text":"from the comatose potential mind that they're looking at"},{"time":139000,"text":"to an actual mind,"},{"time":141000,"text":"which I define simply"},{"time":143000,"text":"as the functioning of the brain"},{"time":145000,"text":"that is remaining inside my head."},{"time":147000,"text":"Now to put this into a broader context,"},{"time":149000,"text":"I want you to imagine that you are an eternal alien"},{"time":152000,"text":"watching the Earth from outer space,"},{"time":154000,"text":"and your favorite show on intergalactic satellite television"},{"time":157000,"text":"is the Earth channel,"},{"time":159000,"text":"and your favorite show is the Human Show."},{"time":162000,"text":"And the reason I think it would be so interesting to you"},{"time":164000,"text":"is because consciousness is so interesting."},{"time":166000,"text":"It's so unpredictable"},{"time":168000,"text":"and so fragile."}]},{"cues":[{"time":170000,"text":"And this is how we began."},{"time":172000,"text":"We all began in the Awash Valley in Ethiopia."},{"time":175000,"text":"The show began with tremendous special effects,"},{"time":177000,"text":"because there were catastrophic climate shifts --"},{"time":180000,"text":"which sort of sounds interesting as a parallel to today."},{"time":183000,"text":"Because of the Earth tilting on its axis"},{"time":185000,"text":"and those catastrophic climate shifts,"},{"time":188000,"text":"we had to figure out how to find better food,"},{"time":190000,"text":"and we had to learn -- there's Lucy; that's how we all began --"},{"time":193000,"text":"we had to learn how to crack open animal bones,"},{"time":196000,"text":"use tools to do that, to feed on the marrow,"},{"time":198000,"text":"to grow our brains more."},{"time":200000,"text":"So we actually grew our consciousness"},{"time":202000,"text":"in response to this global threat."}]},{"cues":[{"time":204000,"text":"Now you also continue to watch"},{"time":206000,"text":"as consciousness evolved to the point"},{"time":208000,"text":"that here in India, in Madhya Pradesh,"},{"time":211000,"text":"there's one of the two oldest known pieces of rock art found."},{"time":215000,"text":"It's a cupule that took 40 to 50,000 blows with a stone tool to create,"},{"time":219000,"text":"and it's the first known expression of art"},{"time":221000,"text":"on the planet."},{"time":223000,"text":"And the reason it connects us with consciousness today"},{"time":225000,"text":"is that all of us still today,"},{"time":227000,"text":"the very first shape we draw as a child"},{"time":230000,"text":"is a circle."},{"time":232000,"text":"And then the next thing we do is we put a dot in the center of the circle."},{"time":235000,"text":"We create an eye --"},{"time":237000,"text":"and the eye that evolves through all of our history."},{"time":239000,"text":"There's the Egyptian god Horus,"},{"time":241000,"text":"which symbolizes prosperity, wisdom and health."},{"time":244000,"text":"And that comes down right way to the present"},{"time":247000,"text":"with the dollar bill in the United States,"},{"time":249000,"text":"which has on it an eye of providence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":252000,"text":"So watching all of this show from outer space,"},{"time":254000,"text":"you think we get it, we understand"},{"time":256000,"text":"that the most precious resource on the blue planet"},{"time":258000,"text":"is our consciousness."},{"time":260000,"text":"Because it's the first thing we draw;"},{"time":262000,"text":"we surround ourselves with images of it;"},{"time":264000,"text":"it's probably the most common image on the planet."},{"time":266000,"text":"But we don't. We take our consciousness for granted."},{"time":269000,"text":"While I was producing in Los Angeles, I never thought about it for a second."},{"time":272000,"text":"Until it was stripped from me, I never thought about it."},{"time":274000,"text":"And what I've learned since that event"},{"time":276000,"text":"and during my recovery"},{"time":278000,"text":"is that consciousness is under threat on this planet"},{"time":281000,"text":"in ways it's never been under threat before."},{"time":283000,"text":"These are just some examples."}]},{"cues":[{"time":285000,"text":"And the reason I'm so honored to be here"},{"time":287000,"text":"to talk today in India"},{"time":289000,"text":"is because India has the sad distinction"},{"time":291000,"text":"of being the head injury capital of the world."},{"time":294000,"text":"That statistic is so sad."},{"time":296000,"text":"There is no more drastic and sudden gap created"},{"time":299000,"text":"between potential and actual mind"},{"time":301000,"text":"than a severe head injury."},{"time":303000,"text":"Each one can entail up to a decade of rehabilitation,"},{"time":306000,"text":"which means that India, unless something changes,"},{"time":308000,"text":"is accumulating a need"},{"time":310000,"text":"for millennia of rehabilitation."},{"time":314000,"text":"What you find in the United States"},{"time":316000,"text":"is an injury every 20 seconds -- that's one and a half million every year --"},{"time":319000,"text":"stroke every 40 seconds,"},{"time":321000,"text":"Alzheimer's disease, every 70 seconds somebody succumbs to that."},{"time":324000,"text":"All of these represent gaps"},{"time":326000,"text":"between potential mind and actual mind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":330000,"text":"And here are some of the other categories, if you look at the whole planet."},{"time":333000,"text":"The World Health Organization tells us"},{"time":335000,"text":"that depression is the number one disease on Earth"},{"time":338000,"text":"in terms of years lived with disability."},{"time":341000,"text":"We find that the number two source of disability"},{"time":344000,"text":"is depression in the age group"},{"time":346000,"text":"of 15 to 44."},{"time":348000,"text":"Our children are becoming depressed"},{"time":350000,"text":"at an alarming rate."},{"time":352000,"text":"I discovered during my recovery"},{"time":354000,"text":"the third leading cause of death amongst teenagers"},{"time":356000,"text":"is suicide."},{"time":358000,"text":"If you look at some of these other items -- concussions."},{"time":360000,"text":"Half of E.R. admissions from adolescents"},{"time":362000,"text":"are for concussions."},{"time":364000,"text":"If I talk about migraine,"},{"time":366000,"text":"40 percent of the population"},{"time":368000,"text":"suffer episodic headaches."},{"time":370000,"text":"Fifteen percent suffer migraines"},{"time":372000,"text":"that wipe them out for days on end."}]},{"cues":[{"time":374000,"text":"All of this is leading -- computer addiction,"},{"time":376000,"text":"just to cover that: the most frequent thing we do"},{"time":378000,"text":"is use digital devices."},{"time":380000,"text":"The average teenager"},{"time":382000,"text":"sends 3,300 texts every [month]."},{"time":385000,"text":"We're talking about a society that is retreating"},{"time":387000,"text":"into depression and disassociation"},{"time":390000,"text":"when we are potentially confronting"},{"time":392000,"text":"the next great catastrophic climate shift."},{"time":395000,"text":"So what you'd be wondering, watching the Human Show,"},{"time":397000,"text":"is are we going to confront and address"},{"time":399000,"text":"the catastrophic climate shift that may be heading our way"},{"time":401000,"text":"by growing our consciousness,"},{"time":403000,"text":"or are we going to continue to retreat?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":405000,"text":"And that then might lead you"},{"time":407000,"text":"to watch an episode one day"},{"time":409000,"text":"of Cedars-Sinai medical center"},{"time":412000,"text":"and a consideration of the difference between potential mind and actual mind."},{"time":415000,"text":"This is a dense array EEG MRI"},{"time":418000,"text":"tracking 156 channels of information."},{"time":420000,"text":"It's not my EEG at Cedars;"},{"time":423000,"text":"it's your EEG tonight and last night."},{"time":426000,"text":"It's the what our minds do every night"},{"time":428000,"text":"to digest the day"},{"time":430000,"text":"and to prepare to bridge from the potential mind when we're asleep"},{"time":432000,"text":"to the actual mind when we awaken the following morning."},{"time":435000,"text":"This is how I was when I returned from the hospital"},{"time":438000,"text":"after nearly four months."},{"time":440000,"text":"The horseshoe shape you can see on my skull"},{"time":442000,"text":"is where they operated and went inside my brain"},{"time":444000,"text":"to do the surgeries they needed to do to rescue my life."},{"time":447000,"text":"But if you look into the eye of consciousness, that single eye you can see,"},{"time":450000,"text":"I'm looking down,"},{"time":452000,"text":"but let me tell you how I felt at that point."},{"time":455000,"text":"I didn't feel empty; I felt everything simultaneously."},{"time":457000,"text":"I felt empty and full, hot and cold,"},{"time":460000,"text":"euphoric and depressed"},{"time":462000,"text":"because the brain is the world's first"},{"time":464000,"text":"fully functional quantum computer;"},{"time":466000,"text":"it can occupy multiple states at the same time."},{"time":469000,"text":"And with all the internal regulators of my brain damaged,"},{"time":472000,"text":"I felt everything simultaneously."}]},{"cues":[{"time":475000,"text":"But let's swivel around and look at me frontally."},{"time":478000,"text":"This is now flash-forward to the point in time"},{"time":480000,"text":"where I've been discharged by the health system."},{"time":483000,"text":"Look into those eyes. I'm not able to focus those eyes."},{"time":485000,"text":"I'm not able to follow a line of text in a book."},{"time":488000,"text":"But the system has moved me on"},{"time":490000,"text":"because, as my family started to discover,"},{"time":493000,"text":"there is no long-term concept"},{"time":495000,"text":"in the health care system."},{"time":497000,"text":"Neurological damage, 10 years of rehab,"},{"time":500000,"text":"requires a long-term perspective."}]},{"cues":[{"time":502000,"text":"But let's take a look behind my eyes."},{"time":504000,"text":"This is a gamma radiation spec scan"},{"time":506000,"text":"that uses gamma radiation"},{"time":508000,"text":"to map three-dimensional function within the brain."},{"time":511000,"text":"It requires a laboratory to see it in three dimension,"},{"time":513000,"text":"but in two dimensions I think you can see"},{"time":515000,"text":"the beautiful symmetry and illumination"},{"time":517000,"text":"of a normal mind at work."},{"time":519000,"text":"Here's my brain."},{"time":521000,"text":"That is the consequence of more than a third of the right side of my brain"},{"time":524000,"text":"being destroyed by the stroke."},{"time":526000,"text":"So my family, as we moved forward"},{"time":528000,"text":"and discovered that the health care system had moved us by,"},{"time":531000,"text":"had to try to find solutions and answers."},{"time":533000,"text":"And during that process -- it took many years --"},{"time":536000,"text":"one of the doctors said that my recovery, my degree of advance,"},{"time":539000,"text":"since the amount of head injury I'd suffered,"},{"time":541000,"text":"was miraculous."},{"time":543000,"text":"And that was when I started to write a book,"},{"time":545000,"text":"because I didn't think it was miraculous."},{"time":547000,"text":"I thought there were miraculous elements,"},{"time":549000,"text":"but I also didn't think it was right"},{"time":551000,"text":"that one should have to struggle and search for answers"},{"time":553000,"text":"when this is a pandemic within our society."}]},{"cues":[{"time":556000,"text":"So from this experience of my recovery,"},{"time":559000,"text":"I want to share four particular aspects --"},{"time":562000,"text":"I call them the four C's of consciousness --"},{"time":564000,"text":"that helped me grow my potential mind"},{"time":567000,"text":"back towards the actual mind that I work with every day."},{"time":570000,"text":"The first C is cognitive training."},{"time":572000,"text":"Unlike the smashed glass of my car,"},{"time":575000,"text":"plasticity of the brain"},{"time":577000,"text":"means that there was always a possibility, with treatment,"},{"time":580000,"text":"to train the brain"},{"time":582000,"text":"so that you can regain and raise your level of awareness and consciousness."},{"time":585000,"text":"Plasticity means that there was always"},{"time":587000,"text":"hope for our reason --"},{"time":589000,"text":"hope for our ability to rebuild that function."},{"time":592000,"text":"Indeed, the mind can redefine itself,"},{"time":594000,"text":"and this is demonstrated by two specialists called Hagen and Silva"},{"time":597000,"text":"back in the 1970's."},{"time":599000,"text":"The global perspective"},{"time":601000,"text":"is that up to 30 percent of children in school"},{"time":603000,"text":"have learning weaknesses"},{"time":605000,"text":"that are not self-correcting,"},{"time":607000,"text":"but with appropriate treatment,"},{"time":609000,"text":"they can be screened for and detected and corrected"},{"time":612000,"text":"and avoid their academic failure."},{"time":614000,"text":"But what I discovered is it's almost impossible to find anyone"},{"time":617000,"text":"who provides that treatment or care."}]},{"cues":[{"time":619000,"text":"Here's what my neuropsychologist provided for me"},{"time":621000,"text":"when I actually found somebody who could apply it."},{"time":624000,"text":"I'm not a doctor, so I'm not going to talk about the various subtests."},{"time":627000,"text":"Let's just talk about full-scale I.Q."},{"time":629000,"text":"Full-scale I.Q. is the mental processing --"},{"time":631000,"text":"how fast you can acquire information,"},{"time":633000,"text":"retain it and retrieve it --"},{"time":635000,"text":"that is essential for success in life today."},{"time":638000,"text":"And you can see here there are three columns."},{"time":640000,"text":"Untestable -- that's when I'm in my coma."},{"time":643000,"text":"And then I creep up to the point that I get a score of 79,"},{"time":646000,"text":"which is just below average."},{"time":649000,"text":"In the health care system, if you touch average, you're done."},{"time":652000,"text":"That's when I was discharged from the system."},{"time":654000,"text":"What does average I.Q. really mean?"},{"time":657000,"text":"It meant that when I was given two and a half hours"},{"time":660000,"text":"to take a test that anyone here"},{"time":662000,"text":"would take in 50 minutes,"},{"time":664000,"text":"I might score an F."},{"time":667000,"text":"This is a very, very low level"},{"time":669000,"text":"in order to be kicked out of the health care system."},{"time":671000,"text":"Then I underwent cognitive training."},{"time":673000,"text":"And let me show you what happened to the right-hand column"},{"time":675000,"text":"when I did my cognitive training over a period of time."},{"time":678000,"text":"This is not supposed to occur."},{"time":681000,"text":"I.Q. is supposed to stabilize and solidify"},{"time":684000,"text":"at the age of eight."}]},{"cues":[{"time":686000,"text":"Now the Journal of the National Medical Association"},{"time":688000,"text":"gave my memoir a full clinical review,"},{"time":690000,"text":"which is very unusual."},{"time":692000,"text":"I'm not a doctor. I have no medical background whatsoever."},{"time":695000,"text":"But they felt the evidences"},{"time":697000,"text":"that there was important, valuable information in the book,"},{"time":700000,"text":"and they commented about it when they gave the full peer review to it."},{"time":703000,"text":"But they asked one question. They said, \"Is this repeatable?\""},{"time":706000,"text":"That was a fair question"},{"time":708000,"text":"because my memoir was simply how I found solutions that worked for me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":711000,"text":"The answer is yes, and for the first time,"},{"time":713000,"text":"it's my pleasure to be able to share two examples."},{"time":715000,"text":"Here's somebody, what they did as they went through cognitive training"},{"time":717000,"text":"at ages seven and 11."},{"time":719000,"text":"And here's another person in, call it, high school and college."},{"time":722000,"text":"And this person is particularly interesting."},{"time":724000,"text":"I won't go into the intrascatter that's in the subtests,"},{"time":726000,"text":"but they still had a neurologic issue."},{"time":728000,"text":"But that person could be identified"},{"time":730000,"text":"as having a learning disability."},{"time":732000,"text":"And with accommodation, they went on to college"},{"time":734000,"text":"and had a full life in terms of their opportunities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":737000,"text":"Second aspect:"},{"time":739000,"text":"I still had crushing migraine headaches."},{"time":741000,"text":"Two elements that worked for me here"},{"time":743000,"text":"are -- the first is 90 percent, I learned, of head and neck pain"},{"time":747000,"text":"is through muscular-skeletal imbalance."},{"time":749000,"text":"The craniomandibular system is critical to that."},{"time":753000,"text":"And when I underwent it and found solutions,"},{"time":756000,"text":"this is the interrelationship between the TMJ and the teeth."},{"time":759000,"text":"Up to 30 percent of the population"},{"time":761000,"text":"have a disorder, disease or dysfunction in the jaw"},{"time":764000,"text":"that affects the entire body."},{"time":766000,"text":"I was fortunate to find a dentist"},{"time":768000,"text":"who applied this entire universe"},{"time":770000,"text":"of technology you're about to see"},{"time":772000,"text":"to establish that if he repositioned my jaw,"},{"time":774000,"text":"the headaches pretty much resolved,"},{"time":776000,"text":"but that then my teeth weren't in the right place."},{"time":778000,"text":"He then held my jaw in the right position"},{"time":780000,"text":"while orthodontically he put my teeth into correct alignment."},{"time":784000,"text":"So my teeth actually hold my jaw in the correct position."},{"time":787000,"text":"This affected my entire body."}]},{"cues":[{"time":790000,"text":"If that sounds like a very, very strange thing to say"},{"time":792000,"text":"and rather a bold statement --"},{"time":794000,"text":"How can the jaw affect the entire body? --"},{"time":796000,"text":"let me simply point out to you,"},{"time":798000,"text":"if I ask you tomorrow"},{"time":800000,"text":"to put one grain of sand between your teeth"},{"time":802000,"text":"and go for a nice long walk,"},{"time":804000,"text":"how far would you last"},{"time":806000,"text":"before you had to remove that grain of sand?"},{"time":808000,"text":"That tiny misalignment."},{"time":810000,"text":"Bear in mind, there are no nerves in the teeth."},{"time":812000,"text":"That's why the same between the before and after that this shows,"},{"time":815000,"text":"it's hard to see the difference."},{"time":817000,"text":"Now just trying putting a few grains of sand between your teeth"},{"time":819000,"text":"and see the difference it makes."},{"time":821000,"text":"I still had migraine headaches."}]},{"cues":[{"time":823000,"text":"The next issue that resolved"},{"time":825000,"text":"was that, if 90 percent of head and neck pain"},{"time":827000,"text":"is caused by imbalance,"},{"time":829000,"text":"the other 10 percent, largely --"},{"time":831000,"text":"if you set aside aneurysms, brain cancer"},{"time":833000,"text":"and hormonal issues --"},{"time":835000,"text":"is the circulation."},{"time":837000,"text":"Imagine the blood flowing through your body --"},{"time":839000,"text":"I was told at UCLA Medical Center --"},{"time":841000,"text":"as one sealed system."},{"time":843000,"text":"There's a big pipe with the blood flowing through it,"},{"time":845000,"text":"and around that pipe are the nerves"},{"time":847000,"text":"drawing their nutrient supply from the blood."},{"time":849000,"text":"That's basically it."},{"time":851000,"text":"If you press on a hose pipe in a sealed system,"},{"time":853000,"text":"it bulges someplace else."},{"time":855000,"text":"If that some place else where it bulges"},{"time":857000,"text":"is inside the biggest nerve in your body, your brain,"},{"time":860000,"text":"you get a vascular migraine."},{"time":862000,"text":"This is a level of pain that's only known"},{"time":864000,"text":"to other people who suffer vascular migraines."},{"time":867000,"text":"Using this technology,"},{"time":869000,"text":"this is mapping in three dimensions."},{"time":871000,"text":"This is an MRI MRA MRV,"},{"time":873000,"text":"a volumetric MRI."},{"time":875000,"text":"Using this technology, the specialists at UCLA Medical Center"},{"time":878000,"text":"were able to identify"},{"time":880000,"text":"where that compression in the hose pipe was occurring."},{"time":882000,"text":"A vascular surgeon removed most of the first rib on both sides of my body."},{"time":886000,"text":"And in the following months and years,"},{"time":888000,"text":"I felt the neurological flow of life itself returning."}]},{"cues":[{"time":891000,"text":"Communication, the next C. This is critical."},{"time":894000,"text":"All consciousness is about communication."},{"time":897000,"text":"And here, by great fortune,"},{"time":899000,"text":"one of my father's clients"},{"time":901000,"text":"had a husband who worked"},{"time":903000,"text":"at the Alfred Mann Foundation for Scientific Research."},{"time":906000,"text":"Alfred Mann is a brilliant physicist and innovator"},{"time":908000,"text":"who's fascinated with bridging gaps in consciousness,"},{"time":911000,"text":"whether to restore hearing to the deaf, vision to the blind"},{"time":914000,"text":"or movement to the paralyzed."},{"time":916000,"text":"And I'm just going to give you an example today"},{"time":918000,"text":"of movement to the paralyzed."},{"time":920000,"text":"I've brought with me, from Southern California,"},{"time":923000,"text":"the FM device."},{"time":925000,"text":"This is it being held in the hand."},{"time":927000,"text":"It weighs less than a gram."},{"time":929000,"text":"So two of them implanted in the body would weigh less than a dime."},{"time":932000,"text":"Five of them would still weigh less"},{"time":934000,"text":"than a rupee coin."}]},{"cues":[{"time":936000,"text":"Where does it go inside the body?"},{"time":938000,"text":"It has been simulated and tested to endure in the body corrosion-free"},{"time":940000,"text":"for over 80 years."},{"time":942000,"text":"So it goes in and it stays there."},{"time":944000,"text":"Here are the implantation sites."},{"time":946000,"text":"The concept that they're working towards -- and they have working prototypes --"},{"time":949000,"text":"is that we placed it throughout the motor points of the body"},{"time":951000,"text":"where they're needed."},{"time":953000,"text":"The main unit will then go inside the brain."},{"time":955000,"text":"An FM device in the cortex of the brain, the motor cortex,"},{"time":958000,"text":"will send signals in real time"},{"time":960000,"text":"to the motor points in the relevant muscles"},{"time":962000,"text":"so that the person will be able to move their arm, let's say, in real time,"},{"time":965000,"text":"if they've lost control of their arm."},{"time":967000,"text":"And other FM devices implanted in fingertips,"},{"time":970000,"text":"on contacting a surface,"},{"time":972000,"text":"will send a message back to the sensory cortex of the brain,"},{"time":975000,"text":"so that the person feels a sense of touch."},{"time":978000,"text":"Is this science fiction? No,"},{"time":980000,"text":"because I'm wearing the first application of this technology."},{"time":983000,"text":"I don't have the ability to control my left foot."},{"time":985000,"text":"A radio device is controlling every step I take,"},{"time":988000,"text":"and a sensor picks up my foot for me"},{"time":990000,"text":"every time I walk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":992000,"text":"And in closing, I want to share"},{"time":994000,"text":"the personal reason why this meant so much to me"},{"time":996000,"text":"and changed the direction of my life."},{"time":998000,"text":"In my coma, one of the presences I sensed"},{"time":1000000,"text":"was someone I felt was a protector."},{"time":1002000,"text":"And when I came out of my coma, I recognized my family,"},{"time":1005000,"text":"but I didn't remember my own past."},{"time":1008000,"text":"Gradually, I remembered the protector was my wife."},{"time":1011000,"text":"And I whispered the good news"},{"time":1013000,"text":"through my broken jaw, which was wired shut,"},{"time":1015000,"text":"to my night nurse."},{"time":1017000,"text":"And the following morning, my mother came to explain"},{"time":1019000,"text":"that I'd not always been in this bed, in this room,"},{"time":1021000,"text":"that I'd been working in film and television"},{"time":1023000,"text":"and that I had been in a crash"},{"time":1025000,"text":"and that, yes, I was married,"},{"time":1028000,"text":"but Marcy had been killed instantly in the crash."},{"time":1031000,"text":"And during my time in coma,"},{"time":1033000,"text":"she had been laid to rest in her hometown of Phoenix."},{"time":1037000,"text":"Now in the dark years that followed, I had to work out what remained for me"},{"time":1040000,"text":"if everything that made today special was gone."},{"time":1043000,"text":"And as I discovered these threats to consciousness"},{"time":1046000,"text":"and how they are surrounding the world"},{"time":1048000,"text":"and enveloping the lives of more and more people every day,"},{"time":1051000,"text":"I discovered what truly remained."},{"time":1053000,"text":"I believe that we can overcome the threats to our consciousness,"},{"time":1056000,"text":"that the Human Show can stay on the air"},{"time":1058000,"text":"for millennia to come."},{"time":1060000,"text":"I believe that we can all rise and shine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1063000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1065000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1071000,"text":"Lakshmi Pratury: Just stay for a second. Just stay here for a second."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1074000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1078000,"text":"You know,"},{"time":1081000,"text":"when I heard Simon's --"},{"time":1085000,"text":"please sit down; I just want to talk to him for a second --"},{"time":1088000,"text":"when I read his book, I went to LA to meet him."},{"time":1091000,"text":"And so I was sitting in this restaurant,"},{"time":1094000,"text":"waiting for a man to come by"},{"time":1097000,"text":"who obviously would have some difficulty ..."},{"time":1099000,"text":"I don't know what I had in my mind."},{"time":1101000,"text":"And he was walking around."},{"time":1103000,"text":"I didn't expect that person that I was going to meet"},{"time":1105000,"text":"to be him."},{"time":1107000,"text":"And then we met and we talked,"},{"time":1109000,"text":"and I'm like, he doesn't look"},{"time":1111000,"text":"like somebody who was built out of nothing."},{"time":1115000,"text":"And then I was amazed"},{"time":1117000,"text":"at what role technology played"},{"time":1119000,"text":"in your recovery."},{"time":1121000,"text":"And we have his book outside"},{"time":1123000,"text":"in the bookshop."},{"time":1125000,"text":"The thing that amazed me"},{"time":1127000,"text":"is the painstaking detail"},{"time":1130000,"text":"with which he has written"},{"time":1132000,"text":"every hospital he has been to,"},{"time":1134000,"text":"every treatment he got,"},{"time":1136000,"text":"every near-miss he had,"},{"time":1139000,"text":"and how accidentally he stumbled upon innovations."},{"time":1143000,"text":"So I think this one detail"},{"time":1148000,"text":"went past people really quick."},{"time":1150000,"text":"Tell a little bit about what you're wearing on your leg."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1153000,"text":"Simon Lewis: I knew when I was timing this"},{"time":1155000,"text":"that there wouldn't be time for me to do anything about --"},{"time":1157000,"text":"Well this is it. This is the control unit."},{"time":1160000,"text":"And this records every single step I've taken"},{"time":1162000,"text":"for, ooh, five or six years now."},{"time":1164000,"text":"And if I do this, probably the mic won't hear it."},{"time":1169000,"text":"That little chirp followed by two chirps is now switched on."},{"time":1172000,"text":"When I press it again, it'll chirp three times,"},{"time":1175000,"text":"and that'll mean that it's armed and ready to go."},{"time":1179000,"text":"And that's my friend. I mean, I charge it every night."},{"time":1182000,"text":"And it works. It works."},{"time":1184000,"text":"And what I would love to add because I didn't have time ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1187000,"text":"What does it do? Well actually, I'll show you down here."},{"time":1190000,"text":"This down here, if the camera can see that,"},{"time":1193000,"text":"that is a small antenna."},{"time":1196000,"text":"Underneath my heel, there is a sensor"},{"time":1199000,"text":"that detects when my foot leaves the ground --"},{"time":1201000,"text":"what's called the heel lift."},{"time":1203000,"text":"This thing blinks all the time; I'll leave it out, so you might be able to see it."},{"time":1206000,"text":"But this is blinking all the time. It's sending signals in real time."},{"time":1209000,"text":"And if you walk faster, if I walk faster,"},{"time":1212000,"text":"it detects what's called the time interval,"},{"time":1214000,"text":"which is the interval between each heel lift."},{"time":1216000,"text":"And it accelerates the amount and level of the stimulation."},{"time":1220000,"text":"The other things they've worked on -- I didn't have time to say this in my talk --"},{"time":1223000,"text":"is they've restored functional hearing"},{"time":1225000,"text":"to thousands of deaf people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1227000,"text":"I could tell you the story: this was going to be an abandoned technology,"},{"time":1230000,"text":"but Alfred Mann met the doctor who was going to retire,"},{"time":1232000,"text":"[Dr. Schindler.]"},{"time":1234000,"text":"And he was going to retire -- all the technology was going to be lost,"},{"time":1237000,"text":"because not a single medical manufacturer would take it on"},{"time":1240000,"text":"because it was a small issue."},{"time":1242000,"text":"But there's millions of deaf people in the world,"},{"time":1245000,"text":"and the Cochlear implant has given hearing to thousands of deaf people now."},{"time":1248000,"text":"It works."},{"time":1250000,"text":"And the other thing is they're working on artificial retinas for the blind."},{"time":1253000,"text":"And this, this is the implantable generation."},{"time":1256000,"text":"Because what I didn't say in my talk"},{"time":1258000,"text":"is this is actually exoskeletal."},{"time":1260000,"text":"I should clarify that."},{"time":1262000,"text":"Because the first generation is exoskeletal,"},{"time":1264000,"text":"it's wrapped around the leg,"},{"time":1266000,"text":"around the affected limb."},{"time":1268000,"text":"I must tell you, they're an amazing --"},{"time":1270000,"text":"there's a hundred people who work in that building --"},{"time":1272000,"text":"engineers, scientists,"},{"time":1274000,"text":"and other team members -- all the time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1276000,"text":"Alfred Mann has set up this foundation"},{"time":1279000,"text":"to advance this research"},{"time":1281000,"text":"because he saw"},{"time":1283000,"text":"there's no way venture capital would come in for something like this."},{"time":1286000,"text":"The audience is too small."},{"time":1288000,"text":"You'd think, there's plenty of paralyzed people in the world,"},{"time":1290000,"text":"but the audience is too small,"},{"time":1292000,"text":"and the amount of research, the time it takes,"},{"time":1295000,"text":"the FDA clearances,"},{"time":1297000,"text":"the payback time is too long"},{"time":1299000,"text":"for V.C. to be interested."},{"time":1301000,"text":"So he saw a need and he stepped in."},{"time":1303000,"text":"He's a very, very remarkable man."},{"time":1306000,"text":"He's done a lot of very cutting-edge science."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1309000,"text":"LP: So when you get a chance, spend some time with Simon."},{"time":1311000,"text":"Thank you. Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1313000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}